sentences.sentence: No one fainted at the sight of the aircraft being trafficked onto the runway.
sentences.translation: 没有人因为看到飞机被贩运到跑道上而晕倒。

sentences.sentence: So far, it has rescued more than 100 trafficked children.
sentences.translation: 迄今为止已经解救了100多名被拐儿童。

sentences.sentence: Tens of thousands are trafficked within their own borders.
sentences.translation: 另外这些国家境内还有成千上万的儿童被贩卖。
